  (@custom "contractspecv0" (after data) "\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07DataKey\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00DCurrent admin address. Instance storage \e2\80\94 lives with the contract.\00\00\00\05Admin\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00GPer-address ZMOKE balance. Persistent storage \e2\80\94 TTL-bumped on access.\00\00\00\00\07Balance\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00FDelegated spending allowance. Temporary storage \e2\80\94 expires by ledger.\00\00\00\00\00\09Allowance\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\10AllowanceDataKey\00\00\00\00\00\00\00iBurn ZMOKE owned by the caller.\0aZmokeAgent calls this when a user redeems 1000 ZMOKE for $1 store credit.\00\00\00\00\00\00\04burn\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04from\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06amount\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\14Mint ZMOKE rewards to an address.\0a\0aOnly callable by the current admin. ZmokeAgent enforces the 10 ZMOKE/$1\0arate upstream \e2\80\94 this contract does not re-validate business logic.\0a\0aAmounts are in the smallest unit (10^decimal):\0amint 10 ZMOKE \e2\86\92 amount = 100_000_000  (10 \c3\97 10^7)\00\00\00\04mint\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02to\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06amount\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04name\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\10\00\00\00\00\00\00\00iReturn the current admin address.\0aExposed so the TypeScript client can confirm distributor configuration.\00\00\00\00\00\00\05admin\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06symbol\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\10\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07approve\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04from\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07spender\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06amount\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\11expiration_ledger\00\00\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07balance\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\